    - If adjacent slices discuss the same core topic, or belong to the same continuous speech/event, **you MUST merge them**.
    - **Ignore** standard camera movements (e.g., Close-up <-> Medium Shot switches, Shot-Reverse-Shot in dialogue).

2.  **Priority 2: Visual Exception (Conditional Split)**
    - Check `ðŸ“·[VIS]` (Visual Description) within the merged range.
