      a. **Flashback / Narrative Cutaway**: The visual environment shifts drastically in time or space (e.g., from "Current Cafe" to "Bedroom in the past").
      b. **Establishing Shot**: A new environment appearing as a standalone shot, marking a new chapter.

3.  **Handling No-Text Slices**
